<body>
<h1> Syntax </h1>
<br>
berserk : incite yourself into a furious battle rage<br>
<br>
<h1> Description </h1>
<br>
This is a skill, exclusively available to warriors, which increases the<br>
amount of damage inflicted with each successful hit.  The amount of<br>
additional damage depends upon skill, level, and while so enraged a<br>
player is incapable of ANY type of flight, and may find himself tired<br>
(but alive) following combat.<br>
